snippet.title: Amber Van Day - Kids In The Corner (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Amber Van Day “Kids In The Corner” available now: 
https://umg.lnk.to/KidsInTheCorner


Follow Amber Van Day on: 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ambervanday/?hl=de 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ambervandaymusic/ 
Universal Artist Page: https://www.universal-music.de/amber-van-day
Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/artist/6NFRBhq9SmNn1FAiRs9AEf
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCUJKv7wZFWC3Sg3QOmZlO8Q/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@ambervandizzle

‘Kids In The Corner’ is the confident and defiant debut single from new London based singer and songwriter Amber Van Day. A self-assured anthem about embracing difference and vulnerability and not adhering to labels, the track is out now on Better Now Records and Island Records.

Music video by Amber Van Day performing Kids In The Corner. © 2020 Amber van Day, under exclusive license to Universal Music GmbH
